Package org.apache.calcite.rel.metadata

Class MetadataFactoryImpl

java.lang.Object
org.apache.calcite.rel.metadata.MetadataFactoryImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
MetadataFactory
@Deprecated public class MetadataFactoryImpl extends Object implements MetadataFactory
Deprecated.
Use RelMetadataQuery.
Implementation of MetadataFactory that gets providers from a RelMetadataProvider and stores them in a cache.

The cache does not store metadata. It remembers which providers can provide which kinds of metadata, for which kinds of relational expressions.
